snippet: Police in Texas responding to a possible suicide at a home in suburban Fort Worth found the bodies of a man, two women and a girl inside the residence, officials said on Monday....

headline.print_headline: Texas Police Investigate Deaths of Four People in Fort Worth Area Home
headline.main: Texas Police Investigate Deaths of Four People in Fort Worth Area Home

lead_paragraph: Police in Texas responding to a possible suicide at a home in suburban Fort Worth found the bodies of a man, two women and a girl inside the residence, officials said on Monday.
